SUMMARY:SuperNova
DESCRIPTION:Since 2015\, Supernova (previously ‘Super Smash Con’) has brought thousands of fans from all over the world together in celebration and competition! \nFor our 10th Anniversary\, we’re going even BIGGER. This year\, we’re aiming to make history together\, with the largest ALL-TIME tournaments for Melee and Rivals 2. \nSome BIG members will be showing game there\, including the multiplayer party RTS Base Battles.
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/supernova/
END:VEVENT
