LAST-MODIFIED:20250806T142511Z
UID:262-1754640000-1754845200@baltimoreindiegames.com
SUMMARY:Otakon
DESCRIPTION:Founded in 1994\, Otakon is an annual convention held in the summer months to celebrate Asian pop culture (anime\, manga\, music\, movies\, video games\, etc) and its fandom. The event runs from Friday to Sunday and is packed with a schedule that has tons to do. \nOtakon is held at the Walter E. Washington Convention Center in our nation’s capital of Washington\, DC. \nSome BIG members will be showing games there\, including Boba Studios showing Squirrely Roo Rabbit.
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/otakon/
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20250816T100000
