CREATED:20250803T014958Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250803T014958Z
UID:258-1756555200-1756573200@baltimoreindiegames.com
SUMMARY:End of Summer Game Dev Picnic in College Park
DESCRIPTION:Come join us for an end of summer picnic at BIG member Stevens Miller’s house in College Park\, between Lackawanna St. and Mangum Rd. on 52nd Ave. Ignore permit parking signs: Stevens will arrange event parking with the city. Greenbelt Metro is 5min walk (last stop on the Green line). This picnic is for all local game devs in the Baltimore-Washington area. \nDetails and RSVP link: https://www.meetup.com/baltimore-indie-game-developers-group/events/310332861
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/end-of-summer-game-dev-picnic-in-college-park/
END:VEVENT
